{"tid":1892004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"研究：因疫情停工兩週 中國碳排放減1億公噸","createTime":"2020-02-22T08:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T09:36:18.000Z","uid":220701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e83d8e296bc8774da94eb71712c5b655767bc63","tid":1892004,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:58:47.000Z","msg":"研究：因疫情停工兩週 中國碳排放減1億公噸<br />\n最新更新：2020/02/20 08:45<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200220/1024x750_739246281542.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200220%2F1024x750_739246281542.jpg&h=985c3dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n芬蘭能源與清潔空氣研究中心19日公布報告指出，中國過去兩週來的碳排放量至少減少了一億公噸。<br />\n（示意圖／圖取自Pixabay圖庫）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社北京19日綜合外電報導）武漢肺炎疫情癱瘓了中國經濟，但也因禍得福。芬蘭能源與清潔空氣研究中心（CREA）今天公布報告指出，中國過去兩週來的碳排放量至少減少了一億公噸。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，這個數字占了去年同期全球碳排放量近6%。這份發表在英國Carbon Brief網站上的研究報告指出，武漢肺炎疫情迅速在中國蔓延，導致煤炭與石油的需求下滑，進而使碳排放量大減。<br />\n<br />\n研究發現，在過去兩週，中國火力發電廠每日發電量若與去年同期相較，下降到4年低點，鋼產量也下滑至5年低點。<br />\n<br />\n研究指出，中國是全世界最大的石油進口與消費國，但石油重鎮山東省的煉油廠產量已下滑至2015年秋季以來最低點。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，中國的經濟活動通常在農曆春節假期過後會開始熱絡，但官方下令包括上海在內的多個省市延後一週復工，好讓人們待在家裡，以利控制武漢肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n報告稱，這些控制疫情的措施導致各重要產業部門的產值減少了15%至40%。「過去兩週很有可能就消除了中國1/4或更多的二氧化碳排放量，而這兩週正常情況下應該是農曆年假後的復工潮。」<br />\n<br />\n但環保人士警告，目前碳排放減少只是一時現象，一旦官方採取振興措施以提高重度污染企業的產量，這些環保收穫就會逆轉。（譯者：陳家倫/核稿：張佑之）1090219<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200220/917x688_058454455391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200220%2F917x688_058454455391.jpg&h=37a8640d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情迅速在中國蔓延，導致煤炭與石油的需求下滑，進而使碳排放量大減。圖為中國近7年春節前後的碳排量，紅線為2020年數據。<br />\n（圖取自Carbon <a href=\"http://Brief網頁carbonbrief.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBrief%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81carbonbrief.org&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=7146f345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Brief網頁carbonbrief.org</a>）<br />\n<br />\n汁: <a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202002190422.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202002190422.aspx&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=392720bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202002190422.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"c36cee19a5eed60d377d57934e499858529490bc","tid":1892004,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"［慶祝夠未］警 世 文！一齊打返起文宣戰線好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"649c82c64176180f99b2c9730ef45cacb3c42470","tid":1892004,"uid":342909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:03:44.000Z","msg":"復工 How dare you <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c6e2a2c61d20e6c8be378ad8093b2908a9ddd2","tid":1892004,"uid":317956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"所以應該一次消滅支那，保護地球"},{"pid":"daea13973894c5561640548206f137d5bad9f254","tid":1892004,"uid":19321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:32:04.000Z","msg":"不錯"},{"pid":"5614a5a969146aaa5633b08f40c7b6050c27c3bb","tid":1892004,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:33:41.000Z","msg":"空氣好晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6914869f0bd7b8c7b8702dd4d870531a44b2193","tid":1892004,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"樓主快啲走,呢度我hold住"},{"pid":"dbfccf071c66efa5b8fc279e651e803f9d6dd4e4","tid":1892004,"uid":234271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22